ÆThe Princess Theatre

Such sweet theatre,
CLAP CLAP the crowd
suddenly screams and claps.

I feel I could stay forever.
Its like having a dream come true,
walking in a wonderland.

A palace of pleasure. Indeed it was.
By Shannon,
Barnes Cray School


